name: Sergeant Edian (V)
Lore: 'Veteran of the Cloud City security forces. Loyal to Administrator Calrissian. Disdainful of the corruption of other Cloud City troopers.',
Text: 'Deploys free to Cloud City. Power +2 in battles you initiate. While present at a battleground, if you just drew an alien (or [Independent] starship for destiny anywhere, may take that card into hand to cancel and redraw that destiny.',
